{
  "info": {
    "name": "citas-api",
    "_postman_id": "c1ta5ap1-0000-4000-8000-000000000001",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "description": "Endpoints de citas-api (clínicas dentales). Auth con JWT RS256 vía header Authorization: Bearer.\n\nUso: corre primero **Auth → Login**; su test guarda el accessToken en la variable de colección `{{token}}` y el resto de requests lo heredan automáticamente.\n\n`base_url` por defecto: http://localhost:8080\n\nCredenciales sembradas (migraciones):\n- ADMIN — admin@mail.com / admin\n- RECEPCIONISTA — recepcion@mail.com / recepcion\n\nLos IDs de ejemplo (1, 2) asumen los datos demo de la migración V7."
  },
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [
      { "key": "token", "value": "{{token}}", "type": "string" }
    ]
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "base_url", "value": "http://localhost:8080" },
    { "key": "token", "value": "" },
    { "key": "refreshToken", "value": "" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Login",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const j = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set(\"token\", j.accessToken);",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set(\"refreshToken\", j.accessToken);"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"admin@mail.com\",\n  \"password\": \"admin\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/auth/login",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "login"]
            },
            "description": "Público. Devuelve { accessToken }. El test de este request lo guarda en {{token}}."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Registrar recepcionista",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"nombre\": \"Ana\",\n  \"email\": \"ana@mail.com\",\n  \"password\": \"ana123\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/auth/register",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "register"]
            },
            "description": "Solo ADMIN. Crea un usuario con rol RECEPCIONISTA. password mínimo 4 caracteres."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Renovar access token",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "body": {
              "mode": "urlencoded",
              "urlencoded": [
                { "key": "refreshToken", "value": "{{refreshToken}}", "type": "text" }
              ]
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/auth/token",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "token"]
            },
            "description": "Público. Renueva el access token a partir de un JWT válido. Devuelve { accessToken }."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
